Javadoc-styl

Core Types
----------
BankService (primary façade)
Customer createCustomer(String name, String pin)
Customer authenticate(String customerId, String pin)
CheckingAccount openChecking(Customer c)
SavingsAccount openSavings(Customer c)
void deposit(BankAccount acct, double amount)
void withdraw(BankAccount acct, double amount)
void transfer(BankAccount from, BankAccount to, double amount)
List<Transaction> getTransactions(BankAccount acct, int limit)

Customer
-------
String getId()
String getName()
List<BankAccount> getAccounts()
Optional<BankAccount> findAccountByNumber(String accountNumber)

BankAccount (abstract)
----------------------
String getAccountNumber()
double getBalance()
AccountType getType()
void apply(Transaction t) (internal)

Transaction
-----------
TransactionType getType() (DEPOSIT/WITHDRAW/TRANSFER)
double getAmount()
String getTimestamp()
String getNote()

Exceptions (recommended)
------------------------
InvalidAmountException (≤ 0 amounts)
InsufficientFundsException
AuthenticationException
NotFoundException
